OL,3,CSchool enters lockdown over 'threats
OL,4,Cto two boys by former pupil'
OL,6,FStudents were placed into lockdown
OL,7,Fafter a credible threat was made to
OL,8,Ftwo boys by a former pupil.
OL,10,FSt Hild's Church of England School, in
OL,11,FHartlepool, announced on social media
OL,12,Fon Monday afternoon (18 March) that it
OL,13,Fhad to enter a "partial lockdown".
OL,15,FThe message read: "Parents please bare
OL,16,Fwith us we need to ensure that the
OL,17,Fchildren remain safe and will update
OL,18,Fas soon as possible."
