OL,3,CSchool enters lockdown over 'threats
OL,4,Cto two boys by former pupil'
OL,6,FA series of updates were shared on the
OL,7,Fschool's Facebook page in the
OL,8,Ffollowing hours, claiming all children
OL,9,Fwere accounted for and safe. The
OL,10,Fnature of the incident was not stated
OL,11,Fonline.
OL,13,FWorried parents and guardians
OL,14,Fcommented and shared the post,
OL,15,Fdemanding further updates on the
OL,16,Fwellbeing of their children.
OL,18,FShortly after 5pm, the school said the
OL,19,Flockdown had been lifted and all
OL,20,Fchildren would be "dismissed from the
OL,21,Fschool site year group by year group".
