OL,3,CSchool enters lockdown over 'threats
OL,4,Cto two boys by former pupil'
OL,6,FIn a statement at 5pm, the force
OL,7,Fconfirmed there was a police presence
OL,8,F"as a matter of precaution following
OL,9,Fsome concerns raised after a threat
OL,10,Fwas made to two boys at the school by
OL,11,Fa former pupil"
OL,13,FIt added: "The school have followed
OL,14,Ftheir own safeguarding procedures and
OL,15,Fhave activated a lockdown at the
OL,16,Fschool whilst officers make enquiries."
